    </content>
    <content lang="en">
      <city>Bern</city>
      <title>SERI News July / August 14</title>
      <lead> Information from the State Secretariat for Education, Research and Innovation SERI</lead>
      <text link="no">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Implementation of the constitutional provisions on education&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Parliament adopts Continuing Education and Training&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VET programmes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;VET programmes: new minimum age for hazardous work&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Higher Education Act (HEdA)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;"The Higher Education Act (HEdA) will create a true legal framework for accreditation"&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Policy area research within the Federal Administration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Revised guidelines adopted to ensure quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;National Innovation Park - new milestone as cantons adopt federally commissioned implementation concept&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Cantons mark a new milestone&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;European joint technology initiative Clean Sky 2 launched&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;More environmentally friendly aircraft thanks to new technologies&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global statement 2014&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Blog on the subject of "Digital Education"&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10 years of swissnex Singapore&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;"Relations have become more complex and more sophisticated"&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automated transfer vehicle (ATV) - fifth mission&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;The Swiss knife of space&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</text>
      <contact>medien@sbfi.admin.ch</contact>
      <link id="125673">
        <title>SERI News July / August 14</title>
        <uri>http://www.sbfi.admin.ch/aktuell/00399/01776/index.html?lang=en</uri>
        <position>Context</position>
      </link>
      <revisions> </revisions>
